 avklart hva prisen p\u00e5 tomta vil bli, om departementet skulle godkjenne. Uansett hvilket valg formannskapet tar, er skoleprosessen forsinket. Tidligst ferdig 2020, sier de n\u00e5."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "f8e3d77f49495651382f79a331c3216d3a3790244ca09debbbbde7843b7b1496"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-08-30T07:24:10.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Etter \u00e5 ha bedt om en ny vurdering av skoletomt p\u00e5 Overvik/Jakobsli har H\u00f8yre konkludert i sitt gruppem\u00f8te mandag."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/article13253701.ece/quzum9/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Ingrid%20Skj%C3%B8tskift%2020160720-HHJ-05.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/18bd7c9a6aa0f91edfd4ef70bad928e13d22f09f.jpg?59121d45"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Dette g\u00e5r H\u00f8yre for i omstridt skoletomtsak -adressa.no", "H\u00f8yre snur ikke", "Avviser spill"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "18bd7c9a6aa0f91edfd4ef70bad928e13d22f09f"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Overvik-utbyggingen", "ingrid skj\u00f8tskift", "Rita Ottervik", "Skole"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Overvik-utbyggingen,ingrid skj\u00f8tskift,Rita Ottervik,Skole"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["vurdering", "ingrid skj\u00f8tskift", "skoletomt", "vedtak", "sak", "skole"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["h\u00f8yre", "overvik", "fylkesmannen", "adresseavisen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "skole"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["hilde opoku", "ingrid skj\u00f8tskift", "rita ottervik", "otta